# WanderWise — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your keys

# ── AI Chatbot (multi-provider, automatic fallback) ───────────────────────────
# The chatbot works WITHOUT any key (uses Pollinations AI free tier automatically).
# Add keys below to use faster/more capable models:

# Option 1: Groq API — fastest, free tier, llama-3.3-70b
# Get key at: https://console.groq.com (free, no credit card)
VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Option 2: Google Gemini — free tier, gemini-2.0-flash
# Get key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey (free)
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Priority order: Groq → Gemini → Pollinations (always free, no key)

# ── All other APIs — FREE, no key needed ─────────────────────────────────────
# Nominatim (OpenStreetMap geocoding)      — free, no key
# Wikipedia / MediaWiki API               — free, no key
# Open-Meteo (weather + climate history)  — free, no key
# Overpass API (OSM heritage/POI data)    — free, no key
# REST Countries API                      — free, no key
# Pollinations AI (LLM fallback)          — free, no key
